name: TreatmentOfHemorrhageOrHematoma
title: Treatment of Hemorrhage or Hematoma
description: Treatment of hemorrhage or hematoma within 35 days from surgery
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Treatment of hemorrhage or hematoma within 35 days from surgery),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Procedure. The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have treatment of hemorrhage or hematoma within 35 days from surgery.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with procedures to control for hemorrhage or hematoma.),(Exclusion Criteria: n/a)
